    "description": "We at Mindspace Business Parks REIT Advisory Limited are looking for an experienced Senior Property Advisor based out of Pimpri-Chinchwad. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Mindspace Business Parks REIT Advisory Limited:\nMindspace Business Parks REIT Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Negotiate pricing, terms, and conditions on behalf of clients\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Sc / M.Sc in Life Sciences\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in Property Valuation\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Project Management\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in Client Relationship Management\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Mindspace Business Parks REIT Advisory Limited!",
